name: I'm not trapped in here with you, you're trapped in here with me
name_original: I'm not trapped in here with you, you're trapped in here with me
description:
Defeat enemies to take their powers, but be careful, you can only use each power once! How long can you keep the CHAIN REACTION going?

Created in 48 hours.

Art by WickedTeaTrickster
